HREF="http://www.courttv.com/download/seminars/form2.html">Submit 
your question or comment to the discussion</i>.</a></p><P><I>To look up the email
address of the lawyers participating in this discussion, use our online directory of
attorneys, <a href="http://www.counsel.com/lawyersearch/">Lawyer Search</a>.

