cryptographic system of digital signatures for the more commercially significant
purposes of authentication and nonrepudiation, where consensus is perhaps more
easily attainable." Charles R. Merrill, "Cryptography for Commerce--Beyond
Clipper," 2 The DateLaw Report No. 2 (Sept 1994), p 4.<p>

