<HtMl><head><title> Court TV Law Center Q & A</title></head><BODY BGCOLOR=ffffff VLINK=FF0005><P align=center><img width=400 height=60 src=/graphics/ctv/qanda/qanda3.gif></P><P align=center><font size=+2><B> Using Mediation to Handle Your Divorce</B></font><BR>With Paula James, Esq. </P><img width=160 height=200 align=left src="/graphics/ctv/qanda/james.gif"><BR><a href=http://www.counsel.com/lawyersearch/j/pjames02.htm>Paula James</a> is  a family law attorney-mediator in Austin, Texas. Afterlitigating divorces and other family law matters for 11 years, Ms. Jamesbegan mediating full-time in 1992. In the last four years, she'smediated approximately 400 divorces.<p><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/bio2.html>More about Ms. James</a><p><a name="tab"><UL></a><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james2.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>What is Mediation?</B></a></P><BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james3.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>Why would I want to mediate my divorce?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james4.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>What does a mediated divorce look like?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james8.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>If we mediate our divorce, do we still have to have our own attorneys?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james5.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>How much does it cost to mediate my divorce?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james6.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>How do I find a mediator?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james7.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>What happens if mediation fails?</B></a></P> <BR><P><a href=/legalhelp/qanda/james/james9.html><IMG border=0  ALIGN=left SRC="/graphics/ctv/redbutt.gif"><B>Ms. James  answers your questions</B></a></P> <BR><P><p><I><B>If you think you need legal advice, you should <a href=/legalhelp/business/lawyer/>consult a lawyer</a>.</B></I> </blockquote></p> </UL><P ALIGN=CENTER><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/stroke.gif" HEIGHT=15 WIDTH=547><BR><A HREF="/map/bottom.map"><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/bottom.gif" ISMAP ALIGN=ABSBOTTOM BORDER=0 WIDTH=533 HEIGHT=30></A><BR><IMG SRC="/graphics/ctv/rights.gif" ALT="Copyright 1995 by the Courtroom Television Network. All Rights Reserved. No parts of this site may be reproduced in any form without permission of Court TV. Disclaimer: Nothing in this site is intended to constitute legal advice"></P></BODY></HTML> 
