<P align=center>
<font size=+2><B>Living Wills</B></font><BR>
With Sally Hurme, Esq. </P><P>


<img  align=left src="/graphics/ctv/qanda/hurme.gif"><BR><PRE>

</PRE> As a lawyer for the American Association of Retired Persons, <a
href=http://www.counsel.com/lawyersearch/h/shurme00.htm>Sally Hurme</a> has designed self-help
courses and a series of legal publications that have helped thousands of people across America to
write a living will.<p>

