PRESIDENT BUT LOST. HE WAS ON THE SCHOOL TENNIS
TEAM, AND WAS RANKED SEVENTH IN THE STATE. HE
WAS ENROLLED AT U.C.L.A. FOR THE FALL, 1989,
SEMESTER BUT NEVER WENT.

