            THE COURT:  Sure.

            MS. WILKINSON:  And they are responsible for their own

   logs.  So in other words, if Agent Williams received it and

   sent it to Agent Burmeister for chemistry and toxicology and

   explosive residue testing, he doesn't send the chain of custody

   form.  He notes it, Agent Burmeister starts his own internal

   chain of custody and sends it back.  So between those two



                                                                           164



   notes, the person's notes, you have a full chain of custody, or

