12   Q.  Would it be fair to say, sir, that you are an outspoken



13   critic of the death penalty?



14   A.  It's no secret that I oppose the death penalty.  I think



15   it's applied unfairly.



16   Q.  And in fact you not only have that belief, but you've



17   spoken about that belief on many, many occasions.



18   A.  Sure.



19   Q.  And you've written about that belief?



20   A.  Yes.



