15   fair trial to occur with more than one capital defendant.



16   A.  I believe so, yes.  Due to the concept of individualized



17   determination as to death or life.



18   Q.  Would that opinion, Mr. Wymore, contrast with the fact that



19   in the last five years, six federal judges have permitted just



20   such an event?



21   A.  Would it contrast with that?  It would contrast with that.



22            MR. MACKEY:  Thank you, Mr. Wymore.



23            THE COURT:  Anything else of the witness,



24   Mr. Thurschwell?



