18   another.  It's indexed in the indexed legal periodicals.



19   That's how I first came across it.  And presumably it is in



20   most libraries.  I assume it's in law libraries and similar



21   places.



22            I think what it means is that maybe you can't be a



23   member of the California Public Defenders' Association, but I'm



