13   BY MR. RYAN:



14   Q.  Please state your full name.



15   A.  Reid Hastie, R-E-I-D, H-A-S-T-I-E.



16   Q.  And your occupation?



17   A.  I'm a professor of psychology at the University of



18   Colorado.



19   Q.  I take it you and your family live in Boulder, Colorado?



20   A.  Yes.



21   Q.  We have given his Honor a copy of your CV, and I'm not



22   going to go through all of the items.  I do want to touch upon



23   a couple of things, however, in your CV.  You have, have you



24   not, served on the boards of professional journals?



25   A.  Yes.







                                                                 157



                           Reid Hastie - Direct



 1   Q.  And what journals are those?



 2   A.  I'm afraid I'd have to look at the CV.  I actually updated



 3   the CV this morning, and I'm on some new editorial boards:



 4   Journal of Consumer Psychology; Journal of Experimental



 5   Psychology, Learning, Memory and Cognition; Journal of



 6   Experimental Psychology, General; Journal of Experimental



