13   A.  Yes.



14   Q.  That's at the top of page 3.



15            Now, you're aware, sir, that sometimes we exclude from



16   jury consideration eyewitness identifications by people that



17   are willing to point to the defendant in court and say he's the



18   one; correct?



19   A.  Yes, that's correct.



20   Q.  And we do that sometimes because the person has made a



21   prior identification under unreliable circumstances; correct?



