15   A.  That's correct.  Exhibit 8 is a -- a more detailed listing



16   that goes through the last names of each of the defendants that



17   were tried before death-qualified juries in each of the



18   judicial districts and then those that received life verdicts



19   and those that received death verdicts.  At the end of Exhibit



20   8, the nine footnotes correspond to numbered note -- notations



